. Career Counselling

I attended a career counselling session on campus with a certified career advisor. We discussed my strengths, potential career paths in IT, and ways to align my studies with long-term goals. I completed a career roadmap during the session.


 STAR TECHNIQUE 
Situation: I was unsure about the career path I should take after graduation.

Task: I needed to gain clarity on which IT field aligned best with my skills and interests.

Action: I booked and attended a career counselling session. I prepared questions beforehand and completed a career goals worksheet during the session.

Result: I identified software development and data analysis as key areas of interest. This helped me choose electives and shape my career direction.
